{"tid":1802791,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遊行嗌港獨根本戇鳩","createTime":"2019-12-29T17:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T17:47:21.000Z","uid":302963,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"21395b6d215cf4ad50cf16f9fd9a8c7867139857","tid":1802791,"uid":302963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"大家諗下，一直以嚟，我哋打住乜嘢旗號去反抗？<br />\n<strong> 民主 自由 人權 人道 等 </strong><br />\n呢啲全部都係普世價值，外國大條道理支持。<br />\n但係你諗下，如果變咗做港獨運動，成件事就變咗中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n我都想香港獨立，但問題唔係遊行嗌出嚟就做到㗎嘛。我哋要做嘅，就係令到每個市民心入面支持，甚至已經當咗香港係獨立，為香港獨立增加資本。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家黃色經濟圈，支持本土，拒絕made in China，呢啲某個程度上都係改變緊市民，支持返香港，拒絕大陸啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家最緊要做嘅嘢，都係做返五大訴求，清算警隊嗰啲。仲有靜靜雞將港獨嘅component植入市民生活。<br />\n<br />\n邊有人小怪都未打完，裝又未拎，直接打boss。<br />\n之後仲講，小怪難度好高，不如直接打boss仲好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人非五毛，不是熱狗。"},{"pid":"59f2d3df5f37c6c5070dabf553cd913b1dd17181","tid":1802791,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:31:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK96ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=e8cf0e82\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ef82fba1bcf24b2d19c6810d00abfc62d5f214ee","tid":1802791,"uid":302963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:33:14.000Z","msg":"搵人應下"},{"pid":"564efe29bf6c883ab8d472cfbfcc8cd65a3cf131","tid":1802791,"uid":302963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T1